revision.text:
{{Userbox
| border-c = rgb(160,175,183)
| id       = [[Image:Wiktionary-logo-v2.svg|38px]]
| id-c     = #fff
| info     = This user is an '''[[:wikt:Wiktionary:Administrators|administrator]]''' on the {{#if:{{{1|}}}|{{{1}}}|[[English Wiktionary]]}}. {{#if:{{{1|}}}
|<span style="font-size:0.9em;" class="plainlinks">([{{fullurl:wikt:{{{lang_code|en}}}:Special:ListUsers|limit=1&username={{urlencode:{{{username|{{BASEPAGENAME}}}}}}}}} <span style="color:#5871C6;">verify{{#if:{{{lang_code|}}}|&nbsp;{{{lang_code}}}|}}</span>])</span>|<span style="font-size:0.9em;" class="plainlinks">([{{fullurl:wikt:Special:ListUsers|limit=1&username={{urlencode:{{{username|{{BASEPAGENAME}}}}}}}}} <span style="color:#5871C6;">verify</span>])</span>}}
| info-c   = #fAf6f6
| usercategory  = Wiktionary administrators
| nocat = {{{nocat|}}}
}}<noinclude>{{doc|content=
By default this template is for the English speaker Wiktionary, to use it for another one, two parameters are needed. <br>Example:
<nowiki>{{User admin Wiktionary|French Wiktionary|lang_code=fr}}</nowiki> gives
{{User admin Wiktionary|French Wiktionary|lang_code=fr|nocat=1}}

[[Category:Wiktionary link templates]]
[[Category:Admin user templates|Admin Wiktionary]]
}}</noinclude>

